data-triple-N3.o: "Carthage College is a four-year private liberal arts college affiliated with the Evangelical Lutheran Church in America. Situated in Kenosha, Wisconsin midway between Chicago, Illinois and Milwaukee, Wisconsin, the campus is on the shore of Lake Michigan and is home to 2,500 full-time and 900 part-time students. Carthage awards the Bachelor of Arts degree with majors in more than 40 subject areas, and the Master of Education degree."@en
